1
00:00:16,150 --> 00:00:17,150
Did you know that that man was a bad guy?

2
00:00:18,150 --> 00:00:21,150
Sometimes I had to do the things that good people don't do.

3
00:00:21,650 --> 00:00:23,150
let me be your choice too.

4
00:00:23,350 --> 00:00:25,150
If you are in trouble, my father can help you.

5
00:00:26,150 --> 00:00:26,850
Who is your father?

6
00:00:27,150 --> 00:00:28,150
You shouldn't know about it.

7
00:00:28,350 --> 00:00:30,150
The two of us can be friends and that's enough.

8
00:00:31,150 --> 00:00:31,850
Stop.

9
00:00:32,150 --> 00:00:34,150
Don't move the body anywhere.

10
00:00:34,650 --> 00:00:37,150
The person who died was a relative of my worker.

11
00:00:37,350 --> 00:00:40,150
He suspected the death of his nephew.

12
00:00:41,150 --> 00:00:42,150
This is not Dong's body.

13
00:00:42,350 --> 00:00:44,150
If it's not Dong's body, whose body is this?

14
00:00:44,450 --> 00:00:47,150
Anyway, I need to bring the body back to check to see what happened.

15
00:00:47,450 --> 00:00:49,150
If there's a progress, I will immediately inform you all.

16
00:00:50,150 --> 00:00:52,150
I'm rich today. It's my treat.

17
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:54,150
Dong's uncle.

18
00:00:55,150 --> 00:00:56,150
Why is he wealthy now?

19
00:00:57,150 --> 00:00:58,150
So how did you handle Dong's body?

20
00:00:58,350 --> 00:01:01,150
The people in the kitchen collecting mushrooms and the workers are there.

21
00:01:01,450 --> 00:01:03,150
It wouldn't be that easy to dig up Dong's body.

22
00:01:03,650 --> 00:01:05,150
But we have to find a way to get rid of the body.

23
00:01:05,850 --> 00:01:07,150
I'll go back and deal with it again soon.

24
00:01:07,450 --> 00:01:09,150
I will find a way to handle that body.

25
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:03,150
The warehouse at the temple was completely burned down?

26
00:03:03,450 --> 00:03:04,150
Yes, sir.

27
00:03:05,150 --> 00:03:08,150
I assumed that the area was bombed last night.

28
00:03:08,650 --> 00:03:10,150
The area has been ravaged by flames.

29
00:03:10,650 --> 00:03:12,150
All corpses that were kept were burned.

30
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:18,150
What about the corpse taken for verification?

31
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:20,150
They all caught fire.

32
00:03:25,150 --> 00:03:27,150
Then we can't prove

33
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:29,150
whose body is it?

34
00:03:29,450 --> 00:03:30,150
Yes, Sir.

35
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:47,150
Since the corpse is burned, we can't find any evidence against them, right?

36
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:49,150
Yes.

37
00:03:50,150 --> 00:03:51,150
I don't know where did they make merit.

38
00:03:52,150 --> 00:03:53,150
Why are they always lucky?

39
00:03:53,550 --> 00:03:55,150
No matter what plan I made, they can get away with it all the time.

40
00:03:56,150 --> 00:04:00,150
I don't know how they could destroy the evidence?

41
00:04:01,150 --> 00:04:04,150
The evidence is no longer there.

42
00:04:04,450 --> 00:04:06,150
What should we do next?

43
00:04:07,150 --> 00:04:09,150
Even if they have a hundred gods protecting them,

44
00:04:09,450 --> 00:04:11,150
I won't give up.

45
00:04:17,150 --> 00:04:18,150
How can I let the culprit get away

46
00:04:19,150 --> 00:04:21,150
without doing anything?

47
00:05:21,150 --> 00:05:22,150
You're here in the account room.

48
00:05:22,650 --> 00:05:25,150
That's why I couldn't find you in the office.

49
00:05:27,150 --> 00:05:29,150
What's the matter?

50
00:05:31,150 --> 00:05:32,150
Look at this.

51
00:05:33,150 --> 00:05:35,150
This is the latest account of this month.

52
00:05:35,450 --> 00:05:38,150
Every business have sent the balance to let Five Dragons Association check.

53
00:05:39,150 --> 00:05:40,150
And this.

54
00:05:41,150 --> 00:05:43,150
These are some copies that I copied from several merchants

55
00:05:44,150 --> 00:05:46,150
that we do business with.

56
00:05:50,150 --> 00:05:51,150
The balances didn't match.

57
00:06:07,150 --> 00:06:08,150
Tian.

58
00:06:30,150 --> 00:06:31,150
Is there anything else?

59
00:06:31,450 --> 00:06:32,150
No.

60
00:06:32,550 --> 00:06:36,150
Purchase orders and the balance reported to the association that didn't match

61
00:06:36,550 --> 00:06:38,150
all belong to Mr. Ma.

62
00:06:40,150 --> 00:06:42,150
This means Mr. Ma is playing tricks on us.

63
00:06:55,150 --> 00:06:56,150
Xiaotong.

64
00:06:58,150 --> 00:07:00,150
You let someone call me to come here,

65
00:07:01,150 --> 00:07:02,150
what's the matter?

66
00:07:03,150 --> 00:07:05,150
I heard that the night when the bomb dropped,

67
00:07:06,150 --> 00:07:10,150
the body that had been swapped with Dong's was completely burned, right?

68
00:07:12,150 --> 00:07:13,150
Right.

69
00:07:14,150 --> 00:07:16,150
The police can't do anything right now

70
00:07:16,550 --> 00:07:18,150
because there is no evidence.

71
00:07:19,150 --> 00:07:20,150
No evidence?

72
00:07:20,450 --> 00:07:23,150
But I think this story won't end easily, Big Brother.

73
00:07:24,150 --> 00:07:27,150
Ma would probably dig up this matter over and over.

74
00:07:28,150 --> 00:07:31,150
I'm worried about you so I invited you to come here today.

75
00:07:32,150 --> 00:07:34,150
I'd like you to meet someone.

76
00:07:36,150 --> 00:07:37,150
Who?

77
00:07:39,150 --> 00:07:40,150
Guys.

78
00:07:42,150 --> 00:07:43,150
Where are you taking me to?

79
00:07:49,150 --> 00:07:50,150
Mr. Song.

80
00:08:03,150 --> 00:08:05,150
Big brother, what's the matter?

81
00:08:06,150 --> 00:08:08,150
Why do you call us to an urgent meeting like this?

82
00:08:10,150 --> 00:08:11,150
Wait for Ma to come here,

83
00:08:12,150 --> 00:08:13,150
we'll listen about it together.

84
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:32,150
Big Brother, Chun.

85
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:34,150
Xiaotong.

86
00:08:38,150 --> 00:08:40,150
I came late again as usual today.

87
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:44,150
Let's start the meeting.

88
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:49,150
Bring him in.

89
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:03,150
What is this?

90
00:09:03,450 --> 00:09:06,150
Big brother, why did you bring Zhan here?

91
00:09:10,150 --> 00:09:11,150
Zhan.

92
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:15,150
How were you related to Dong's death?

93
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:19,150
Tell me the truth.

94
00:09:31,150 --> 00:09:34,150
I received money from Mr. Ma.

95
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:38,150
In fact, I wasn't a relative of Dong.

96
00:09:39,150 --> 00:09:41,150
We've once lived in the same village. That's all.

97
00:09:46,150 --> 00:09:51,150
Mr. Ma wanted this to hurt you, Sir.

98
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:55,150
And he'll take the opportunity to become the head of the Five Dragons Association.

99
00:09:55,450 --> 00:09:56,150
He's lying.

100
00:09:57,150 --> 00:10:00,150
He told me that he was Dong's relative.

101
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:05,150
He asked me to help investigate his death.

102
00:10:06,150 --> 00:10:07,150
How dare you?

103
00:10:08,150 --> 00:10:10,150
Slandering me, huh? Idiot.

104
00:10:10,350 --> 00:10:11,150
That's enough.

105
00:10:11,350 --> 00:10:12,150
Bastard.

106
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:17,150
Big Brother, he lied.

107
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:21,150
He's mad that I paid him less.

108
00:10:21,550 --> 00:10:22,150
Bastard.

109
00:10:27,150 --> 00:10:28,150
I have a doubt.

110
00:10:29,150 --> 00:10:33,150
I want to know if anyone else know about this.

111
00:10:34,150 --> 00:10:36,150
Because this is domestic matter.

112
00:10:36,450 --> 00:10:38,150
Only the insiders will know.

113
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:40,150
Zhan.

114
00:10:41,150 --> 00:10:43,150
Has anyone collaborated with you?

115
00:10:43,450 --> 00:10:46,150
I'm not sure, but I heard that…

116
00:10:47,150 --> 00:10:49,150
A madam has told us.

117
00:10:49,350 --> 00:10:50,150
Is it Madam Chan?

118
00:10:51,150 --> 00:10:52,150
Is this woman?

119
00:11:09,150 --> 00:11:10,150
Let go of me.

120
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:15,150
Chan has nothing to do with it.

121
00:11:16,150 --> 00:11:20,150
Have you forgotten that the area that I am in charge of

122
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:22,150
includes a coffin shop?

123
00:11:23,150 --> 00:11:26,150
The employees at the shop were talking about Dong's death

124
00:11:26,450 --> 00:11:28,150
because he learned the secret of Tian.

125
00:11:29,150 --> 00:11:31,150
What is the secret?

126
00:11:31,450 --> 00:11:32,150
And what did he know?

127
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:35,150
Why did you have to shut his mouth?

128
00:11:36,150 --> 00:11:38,150
There's no such secret.

129
00:11:38,450 --> 00:11:40,150
And I didn't kill Dong.

130
00:11:42,150 --> 00:11:44,150
You denied, then I deny as well.

131
00:11:44,550 --> 00:11:47,150
There is no evidence for this matter. The end.

132
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:22,150
Tian, Yang, where are you going?

133
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:24,150
What are the stuff you are carrying?

134
00:12:26,150 --> 00:12:27,150
Come with me.

135
00:12:27,450 --> 00:12:28,150
Be careful.

136
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:33,150
Big Brother, I think this starts to get out of hands.

137
00:12:34,150 --> 00:12:37,150
Give me some time. I will find evidence to prove myself

138
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:40,150
that Zhan is slandering me.

139
00:12:41,150 --> 00:12:43,150
Don't make judgments about things that don't have evidence.

140
00:12:44,150 --> 00:12:46,150
It will destroy the relationship between us,

141
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:49,150
Five Dragons Association.

142
00:12:59,150 --> 00:13:01,150
What if there is evidence for other matter?

143
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:22,150
We found the association's accounting documents.

144
00:13:22,450 --> 00:13:23,150
There are many points that do not match.

145
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:28,150
Most businesses in question all belong to Mr. Ma.

146
00:13:30,150 --> 00:13:32,150
Do you say that I'm cheating?

147
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:45,150
If it isn't,

148
00:13:46,150 --> 00:13:47,150
please explain about it.

149
00:13:52,150 --> 00:13:56,150
This is a coffee business account document sent to the association.

150
00:13:56,550 --> 00:13:58,150
It can be seen that there is a consistent income every year.

151
00:13:59,150 --> 00:14:02,150
But when checking from the total amount from the copies of the merchant's order,

152
00:14:03,150 --> 00:14:05,150
you can see that there are many points that don't match.

153
00:14:09,150 --> 00:14:10,150
Tian.

154
00:14:11,150 --> 00:14:12,150
Let me see it.

155
00:14:13,150 --> 00:14:16,150
Here, Father, this page.

156
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:18,150
Where?

157
00:14:31,150 --> 00:14:32,150
Ma.

158
00:14:34,150 --> 00:14:35,150
You ordered more products

159
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:39,150
and sold for a profit without deducting money to the association?

160
00:14:39,550 --> 00:14:40,150
That's not true.

161
00:14:41,150 --> 00:14:42,150
I wouldn't do that.

162
00:14:44,150 --> 00:14:46,150
You can deny it.

163
00:14:47,150 --> 00:14:49,150
If this evidence is not enough,

164
00:14:50,150 --> 00:14:53,150
I'll find more evidence and uncover everything as soon as possible.

165
00:14:55,150 --> 00:14:56,150
Sir.

166
00:14:57,150 --> 00:15:02,150
Traders should be honest and do what they promise.

167
00:15:03,150 --> 00:15:05,150
If you prioritize your own benefit like this,

168
00:15:06,150 --> 00:15:09,150
no one will respect you in the future.

169
00:15:09,350 --> 00:15:10,150
Tian! / Stop!

170
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:21,150
Ma, move back

171
00:15:33,150 --> 00:15:34,150
and listen to me carefully.

172
00:15:37,150 --> 00:15:40,150
Until Tian finds more evidence,

173
00:15:41,150 --> 00:15:43,150
I will let Xiaotong

174
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:47,150
take care of all coffee businesses instead.

175
00:15:48,150 --> 00:15:51,150
As for the opening of the furniture rental shop that you've proposed last time,

176
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:55,150
I will make Xiaotong take responsibility as well.

177
00:15:56,150 --> 00:15:57,150
Big Brother!

178
00:15:57,450 --> 00:16:00,150
Big Brother, thanks for the opportunity.

179
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:04,150
I will take care of all Ma's works as best as I can.

180
00:16:07,150 --> 00:16:08,150
Ma.

181
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,150
Don't be angry with me.

182
00:16:42,150 --> 00:16:45,150
My heart almost stopped just now, Madam.

183
00:16:45,550 --> 00:16:47,150
Yeah, I thought I would be in trouble.

184
00:16:48,150 --> 00:16:50,150
Mr. Ma is a good man actually.

185
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:52,150
He didn't blame us.

186
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:56,150
What's the matter? Knock on the door first next time.

187
00:16:56,350 --> 00:16:57,150
No manners.

188
00:16:58,150 --> 00:17:01,150
Mr. Song and Madam Li call for you.

189
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:33,150
What's the matter, Sir?

190
00:17:37,150 --> 00:17:40,150
Ma has informed the authorities about Dong's death.

191
00:17:42,150 --> 00:17:43,150
Do you know anything about it?

192
00:17:44,150 --> 00:17:46,150
I don't know.

193
00:17:47,150 --> 00:17:52,150
If you don't know, then why would someone like Ma defended you?

194
00:17:52,450 --> 00:17:53,150
Don't accuse me.

195
00:17:54,150 --> 00:17:56,150
No one defend me at all.

196
00:17:57,150 --> 00:17:59,150
And I really don't know about this.

197
00:18:00,150 --> 00:18:03,150
And how could Ma know about this?

198
00:18:04,150 --> 00:18:06,150
If you didn't tell Ma,

199
00:18:07,150 --> 00:18:10,150
Then why would you meddle in Dong's funeral in the first place?

200
00:18:12,150 --> 00:18:13,150
At the temple,

201
00:18:14,150 --> 00:18:16,150
you were the one who tell everyone you got a nightmare.

202
00:18:17,150 --> 00:18:19,150
Saying you wanted everyone to go to the temple to make merit for Dong.

203
00:18:21,150 --> 00:18:25,150
When it was cremation time, you stalled like you were waiting for someone to come.

204
00:18:27,150 --> 00:18:31,150
When we opened the coffin, the body decayed and no one wanted to see it.

205
00:18:32,150 --> 00:18:33,150
You focused on it.

206
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:36,150
Until you were sure that it might not be Dong's body.

207
00:18:38,150 --> 00:18:41,150
Is this the one who said that she didn't know anything, Sir.

208
00:18:42,150 --> 00:18:43,150
Don't listen to her.

209
00:18:44,150 --> 00:18:46,150
Just a mere speculation, no evidence.

210
00:18:49,150 --> 00:18:50,150
And if there is evidence,

211
00:18:52,150 --> 00:18:53,150
How do you want me to punish you?

212
00:19:00,150 --> 00:19:02,150
Answer me, Chan.

213
00:19:02,450 --> 00:19:03,150
I don't know.

214
00:19:04,150 --> 00:19:06,150
I didn't do it. How can there be evidence?

215
00:19:09,150 --> 00:19:11,150
Right, there is no evidence.

216
00:19:13,150 --> 00:19:15,150
But if something like this happens again,

217
00:19:16,150 --> 00:19:18,150
you prepare to get out of here.

218
00:19:19,150 --> 00:19:21,150
I won't care about any evidence no more.

219
00:19:22,150 --> 00:19:24,150
Who made the Song family in trouble,

220
00:19:25,150 --> 00:19:27,150
I wouldn't let that person survive.

221
00:19:45,150 --> 00:19:46,150
Tian.

222
00:19:47,150 --> 00:19:48,150
Do you dare to have a fight with me?

223
00:19:49,150 --> 00:19:52,150
You will soon know that the person who thought of being my enemy,

224
00:19:53,150 --> 00:19:55,150
will meet what kind of ending.

225
00:20:00,150 --> 00:20:02,150
Goddamn punk.

226
00:20:05,150 --> 00:20:08,150
Mother, I brought you some drink and snacks.

227
00:20:09,150 --> 00:20:11,150
Please have some.

228
00:20:14,150 --> 00:20:17,150
I didn't arrive in time, but I heard from Uncle Bao that

229
00:20:18,150 --> 00:20:21,150
it was Mr. Ma who did all these.

230
00:20:21,550 --> 00:20:23,150
Letting someone else pretend to be Dong's relative

231
00:20:24,150 --> 00:20:25,150
and ruining our family's reputation.

232
00:20:30,150 --> 00:20:31,150
I'm sorry

233
00:20:31,450 --> 00:20:35,150
that I previously kept blaming and had doubts in you.

234
00:20:39,150 --> 00:20:40,150
It's okay.

235
00:20:42,150 --> 00:20:44,150
Dong's matter is over.

236
00:20:47,150 --> 00:20:50,150
Now Mr. Ma must be very angry with us.

237
00:20:52,150 --> 00:20:58,150
And now you are interfering with Mr. Ma's fraud.

238
00:20:59,150 --> 00:21:01,150
You have to be very careful.

239
00:21:04,150 --> 00:21:05,150
Yes, Mother.

240
00:21:06,150 --> 00:21:09,150
I'll be careful. Don't worry.

241
00:21:14,150 --> 00:21:17,150
You can't stop me from worrying about you.

242
00:21:21,150 --> 00:21:22,150
But no matter what,

243
00:21:24,150 --> 00:21:26,150
I will protect you.

244
00:21:28,150 --> 00:21:30,150
And I want you to know that

245
00:21:31,150 --> 00:21:33,150
everything I do,

246
00:21:35,150 --> 00:21:37,150
or what I forbid you from doing whatever you want,

247
00:21:40,150 --> 00:21:44,150
I did it for you.

248
00:21:53,150 --> 00:21:54,150
I love you, Mother.

249
00:22:10,150 --> 00:22:11,150
Bitch.

250
00:22:12,150 --> 00:22:15,150
I really want to kill her. Why does Heaven always take sides with her?

251
00:22:19,150 --> 00:22:23,150
But a woman like me won't give up easily.

252
00:22:37,150 --> 00:22:39,150
I heard that Dad punished you and won't let you cause any more trouble.

253
00:22:41,150 --> 00:22:43,150
And this time he was very angry.

254
00:22:43,450 --> 00:22:45,150
He seems very serious.

255
00:22:46,150 --> 00:22:48,150
Have you seen what Mr. Ma is like?

256
00:22:49,150 --> 00:22:50,150
He didn't blame you this time

257
00:22:51,150 --> 00:22:53,150
because he may keep you for any use in the future.

258
00:22:54,150 --> 00:22:57,150
I don't want you to be at a disadvantage.

259
00:22:58,150 --> 00:23:02,150
But you want to see me being inferior to Madam Li for the rest of your life?

260
00:23:02,450 --> 00:23:03,150
Huh?

261
00:23:05,150 --> 00:23:09,150
You saw that she was always oppressing me.

262
00:23:09,550 --> 00:23:12,150
So am I wrong that I want to have some power as well?

263
00:23:13,150 --> 00:23:14,150
What I do,

264
00:23:15,150 --> 00:23:18,150
I'm not doing it for myself, I'm doing it for you. Remember it.

265
00:23:18,350 --> 00:23:20,150
I know, I've always known.

266
00:23:21,150 --> 00:23:23,150
You've been talking to me since I was a child.

267
00:23:23,550 --> 00:23:24,150
Right.

268
00:23:26,150 --> 00:23:28,150
You never helped me.

269
00:23:29,150 --> 00:23:30,150
So I have to find my own way.

270
00:23:33,150 --> 00:23:34,150
What are you doing?

271
00:23:36,150 --> 00:23:38,150
If Tian has a secret,

