543
00:45:30,750 --> 00:45:31,750
But he didn't contact me.

544
00:45:34,750 --> 00:45:35,750
If he was here,

545
00:45:37,750 --> 00:45:38,750
he would be able to help take care of me.

546
00:45:40,750 --> 00:45:42,750
I don't know if we'll meet again in this life.

547
00:45:46,750 --> 00:45:48,750
And what about you?

548
00:45:49,350 --> 00:45:50,750
Why do you ask about him?

549
00:45:51,750 --> 00:45:52,750
Right.

550
00:45:58,750 --> 00:46:01,750
Why do you suddenly ask about Doctor Qi?

551
00:46:02,750 --> 00:46:04,750
It's nothing, Madam.

552
00:46:05,750 --> 00:46:07,750
Just thinking about the old times.

553
00:46:12,750 --> 00:46:14,750
I thought there was something else.

554
00:46:19,750 --> 00:46:20,750
Li.

555
00:46:21,750 --> 00:46:23,750
It's a matter of my health.

556
00:46:24,750 --> 00:46:26,750
We talk about health and then Bua thought of Doctor Qi.

557
00:46:27,750 --> 00:46:28,750
Saying he was good at herbs.

558
00:46:30,750 --> 00:46:32,750
If he was still here, he would be able to help take care of me.

559
00:46:35,750 --> 00:46:39,750
Oh, if that's the case, let Jia take care of it.

560
00:46:40,350 --> 00:46:43,750
She also learned a lot about medicinal herbs from Doctor Qi.

561
00:46:43,950 --> 00:46:45,750
She's equally talented.

562
00:47:03,750 --> 00:47:05,750
We have to find the right time to destroy that mushroom.

563
00:47:06,750 --> 00:47:08,750
Otherwise, the workers would not stop collecting and eating them.

564
00:47:09,750 --> 00:47:10,750
Hurry up and deal with it.

565
00:47:11,750 --> 00:47:14,750
I will summon the workers who built the bunker to have meal.

566
00:47:15,250 --> 00:47:16,750
This can delay them for an hour.

567
00:47:17,750 --> 00:47:19,750
It can be done in ten minutes.

568
00:47:20,750 --> 00:47:23,750
Just pouring the fermented water specially made by me.

569
00:47:24,250 --> 00:47:25,750
I guarantee that there will be no remains.

570
00:47:35,750 --> 00:47:37,750
Let's take a break.

571
00:47:38,750 --> 00:47:40,750
Today, Madam Li provides another meal for us.

572
00:47:41,750 --> 00:47:44,750
She told us to come and eat them all. Let's go quickly.

573
00:47:45,150 --> 00:47:45,750
Put things down first.

574
00:47:46,750 --> 00:47:47,750
Go.

575
00:48:40,750 --> 00:48:42,750
Did Madam Li hear you ask for Doctor Qi?

576
00:48:43,250 --> 00:48:44,750
Yes, and she acted strangely too.

577
00:48:45,050 --> 00:48:47,750
But when Mr. Song said he was sick, so he thought of Doctor Qi,

578
00:48:48,750 --> 00:48:50,750
Madam Li did not investigate anything further.

579
00:48:53,750 --> 00:48:55,750
Doctor Qi is living in Chonburi.

580
00:48:56,750 --> 00:48:58,750
we can't find him right now.

581
00:49:00,750 --> 00:49:03,750
If we meet Doctor Qi, we'll know what mushroom it is,

582
00:49:04,750 --> 00:49:05,750
and if it has anything to do with the mystery in our home.

583
00:49:08,750 --> 00:49:10,750
What is this?

584
00:49:18,750 --> 00:49:20,750
Auntie, what's up?

585
00:49:22,750 --> 00:49:24,750
Why are all the mushrooms dead?

586
00:49:25,750 --> 00:49:27,750
That's right, they were still fine yesterday.

587
00:49:28,750 --> 00:49:31,750
Let's see if we can still eat them.

588
00:49:32,050 --> 00:49:32,750
Wait! / No!

589
00:49:57,750 --> 00:49:58,750
The worms are all dead as well?

590
00:50:01,750 --> 00:50:03,750
Has anyone watered and plowed the soil here?

591
00:50:04,750 --> 00:50:07,750
No, we just leave it as it is.

592
00:50:07,950 --> 00:50:09,750
It grows well naturally.

593
00:50:12,750 --> 00:50:13,750
That's really strange.

594
00:50:54,750 --> 00:50:55,750
Have we searched the entire place yet?

595
00:50:58,750 --> 00:50:59,750
Yes.

596
00:51:00,750 --> 00:51:02,750
What we haven't done yet is to dig the ground around the palace to find treasures.

597
00:51:04,750 --> 00:51:07,750
Even selling the treasures wouldn't be enough to redeem the palace from Aunt Li.

598
00:51:08,750 --> 00:51:09,750
Madam.

599
00:51:10,750 --> 00:51:12,750
Why do you try to get money to redeem the palace back?

600
00:51:14,750 --> 00:51:16,750
Well, I don't want to marry Tian.

601
00:51:18,750 --> 00:51:21,750
Oh, is it because of Mr. Yang?

602
00:51:22,750 --> 00:51:23,750
Noi.

603
00:51:24,750 --> 00:51:25,750
How do you know it?

604
00:51:26,750 --> 00:51:28,750
Am I that easy to read?

605
00:51:29,750 --> 00:51:32,750
Lady, I have seen you since you were little.

606
00:51:33,250 --> 00:51:36,750
Who do I not know if you love or hate someone?

607
00:51:42,750 --> 00:51:46,750
At first, I thought that if I marry Tian, I would be fine.

608
00:51:47,250 --> 00:51:49,750
Even if we don't love each other now, we'll love each other eventually.

609
00:51:51,750 --> 00:51:54,750
And it's also one way that we can redeem our palace back.

610
00:51:57,750 --> 00:51:58,750
But when...

611
00:52:00,750 --> 00:52:04,750
But when you meet someone who truly loves you, you want to fight for it, right?

612
00:52:05,750 --> 00:52:09,750
I'll fight for it. Fight for my own way of life.

613
00:52:11,750 --> 00:52:13,750
That's my lady.

614
00:52:17,750 --> 00:52:18,750
Pin.

615
00:52:21,750 --> 00:52:24,750
Dress up pretty and cute tomorrow.

616
00:52:25,250 --> 00:52:26,750
I will take you out to have a meal.

617
00:52:53,750 --> 00:52:54,750
Sir.

618
00:52:56,750 --> 00:52:58,750
I didn't visit you at all. I'm sorry.

619
00:52:59,750 --> 00:53:01,750
I don't have much time. The work is too busy.

620
00:53:03,750 --> 00:53:04,750
It's okay.

621
00:53:05,750 --> 00:53:10,750
Today I made an appointment because I wanted to talk about Tian and Pin.

622
00:53:11,750 --> 00:53:14,750
I'd like to tell you that I already have an auspicious time.

623
00:53:18,750 --> 00:53:21,750
I am so excited that I choked.

624
00:53:22,750 --> 00:53:24,750
When is it?

625
00:53:25,150 --> 00:53:25,750
A month and a half.

626
00:53:26,250 --> 00:53:27,750
A month and a half?

627
00:53:34,750 --> 00:53:35,750
Isn't that too fast?

628
00:53:36,750 --> 00:53:37,750
It's too soon.

629
00:53:38,750 --> 00:53:40,750
I'm afraid that I can't prepare in time.

630
00:53:41,750 --> 00:53:42,750
What prepare?

631
00:53:43,750 --> 00:53:45,750
That's good, Madam Li.

632
00:53:46,750 --> 00:53:48,750
I think what Pin said is correct.

633
00:53:49,450 --> 00:53:51,750
It's a bit early.

634
00:53:52,250 --> 00:53:54,750
We should give her a little more time.

635
00:53:55,250 --> 00:53:56,750
Wow, look.

636
00:53:57,150 --> 00:53:59,750
These two kids get along like a house on fire.

637
00:54:00,250 --> 00:54:02,750
This is good.

638
00:54:03,750 --> 00:54:04,750
The auspicious time for wedding

639
00:54:05,750 --> 00:54:06,750
can't be postponed.

640
00:54:07,750 --> 00:54:08,750
Right. Let's do as what you said.

641
00:54:10,750 --> 00:54:11,750
I'm very pleased, no problem at all.

642
00:54:12,250 --> 00:54:13,750
You can handle it, Madam.

643
00:54:14,750 --> 00:54:15,750
If you agree to this,

644
00:54:16,750 --> 00:54:18,750
let's talk about the bride price now.

645
00:54:18,750 --> 00:54:19,750
Bride price?

646
00:54:22,750 --> 00:54:23,750
Tian.

647
00:54:24,750 --> 00:54:25,750
Take Pin out for a walk.

648
00:54:26,550 --> 00:54:28,750
The adults will talk about preparing for the wedding.

649
00:54:29,750 --> 00:54:30,750
You two will be bored.

650
00:54:31,750 --> 00:54:32,750
Yes, Mother.

651
00:54:38,750 --> 00:54:39,750
Thanks.

652
00:54:45,750 --> 00:54:47,750
Don't worry about your palace.

653
00:54:48,350 --> 00:54:51,750
I will give it as a wedding gift for our children.

654
00:54:52,150 --> 00:54:52,750
Is it good?

655
00:54:53,750 --> 00:54:55,750
A lot.

656
00:54:56,750 --> 00:54:57,750
Thank you very much.

657
00:54:58,750 --> 00:55:01,750
And if you have anything to suggest, you can tell me.

658
00:55:02,750 --> 00:55:04,750
Thank you very much, Sir.

659
00:55:05,750 --> 00:55:06,750
We only have a month and a half left.

660
00:55:07,250 --> 00:55:08,750
I won't be able to find the money to redeem the palace in time.

661
00:55:10,750 --> 00:55:13,750
I've tried to stop Mother and Father already, but they didn't listen to me.

662
00:55:18,750 --> 00:55:19,750
Pin, Tian.

663
00:55:20,750 --> 00:55:22,750
Nangnoi said that you will get married tomorrow?

664
00:55:23,750 --> 00:55:26,750
Not tomorrow, but another month and a half.

665
00:55:26,950 --> 00:55:28,750
What? Nangnoi said that…

666
00:55:28,950 --> 00:55:30,750
I was afraid that you would arrive late

667
00:55:31,750 --> 00:55:32,750
so I lied that she was getting married tomorrow.

668
00:55:34,750 --> 00:55:36,750
You ran and didn't even wait for me.

669
00:55:36,950 --> 00:55:37,750
Nangnoi.

670
00:55:38,150 --> 00:55:38,750
Alright.

671
00:55:39,750 --> 00:55:40,750
Now,

672
00:55:41,750 --> 00:55:43,750
whether it's a month and a half or tomorrow, it's no different.

673
00:55:44,050 --> 00:55:45,750
And where will we find the money?

674
00:55:46,750 --> 00:55:47,750
Tian.

675
00:55:48,750 --> 00:55:49,750
Why is Madam in such a hurry?

676
00:55:50,050 --> 00:55:53,750
She wants me to get married so that I can succeed Father.

677
00:55:57,750 --> 00:55:59,750
How are we going to interrupt the wedding?

678
00:56:04,750 --> 00:56:06,750
Oh, I have an idea.

679
00:56:08,750 --> 00:56:10,750
Lady Pin and Mr. Tian, you guys just get married

680
00:56:11,750 --> 00:56:12,750
to deceive your parents first.

681
00:56:13,750 --> 00:56:14,750
No, we can't do that.

682
00:56:15,750 --> 00:56:17,750
If I and Pin get married,

683
00:56:18,750 --> 00:56:21,750
my parents will definitely rush me into having an heir.

684
00:56:25,750 --> 00:56:27,750
We need hundreds of thousands baht to redeem the palace.

685
00:56:28,750 --> 00:56:31,750
Even if I help with my saving, it's not enough anyway.

686
00:56:33,750 --> 00:56:35,750
Using the company's money?

687
00:56:37,750 --> 00:56:38,750
Mother must know it for sure.

688
00:56:42,750 --> 00:56:43,750
Pin.

689
00:56:44,750 --> 00:56:48,750
No matter what, I'll interrupt your wedding.

690
00:56:54,750 --> 00:56:57,750
Tian, but if you are not married yet,

691
00:56:58,250 --> 00:56:59,750
you won't be able to inherit from Father.

692
00:57:01,750 --> 00:57:02,750
Forget about that.

693
00:57:03,750 --> 00:57:04,750
My brother's happiness must come first.

694
00:57:12,750 --> 00:57:14,750
Pin, if we think positively,

695
00:57:15,750 --> 00:57:17,750
we still have a month and a half left

696
00:57:18,250 --> 00:57:20,750
to figure out how to get money to redeem the palace.

697
00:57:21,750 --> 00:57:22,750
Then you won't have to get married.

698
00:57:39,750 --> 00:57:40,750
Mother.

699
00:57:41,750 --> 00:57:42,750
Mother.

700
00:58:56,750 --> 00:58:57,750
Here it is.

701
00:58:59,750 --> 00:59:00,750
Pin's title deed.

702
00:59:27,750 --> 00:59:28,750
Mother.

703
00:59:36,750 --> 00:59:37,750
Do you have to do this?

704
00:59:39,750 --> 00:59:40,750
It's not like that, Mother.

705
00:59:41,750 --> 00:59:43,750
I just want to come and check

706
00:59:44,750 --> 00:59:46,750
the mortgage contract and Pin's palace deed

707
00:59:47,750 --> 00:59:49,750
whether it's correct.

708
00:59:50,750 --> 00:59:51,750
You don't have to worry about that.

709
00:59:52,750 --> 00:59:54,750
Mortgage contract and Pin's palace deed

710
00:59:55,750 --> 00:59:56,750
is legal.

711
00:59:57,750 --> 00:59:59,750
There were witnesses and the seal is correct.

712
01:00:00,750 --> 01:00:01,750
Therefore,

713
01:00:02,750 --> 01:00:04,750
even if someone steals it back to Pin,

714
01:00:05,750 --> 01:00:07,750
it is useless.

715
01:00:09,750 --> 01:00:11,750
You don't want to marry Lady Pin

716
01:00:12,750 --> 01:00:13,750
to the point where you have to steal the title deed and return it to her?

717
01:00:15,750 --> 01:00:17,750
I pity her.

718
01:00:19,750 --> 01:00:21,750
If you have pity on her, that's good.

719
01:00:22,750 --> 01:00:24,750
Just get married to her.

720
01:00:25,750 --> 01:00:28,750
Once you get married, she'll get her palace back.

721
01:00:31,750 --> 01:00:33,750
I pity her

722
01:00:34,750 --> 01:00:36,750
because she has to marry someone who didn't love her.

723
01:00:39,750 --> 01:00:40,750
And you know what I am.

724
01:00:40,750 --> 01:00:41,950
I know it.

725
01:00:43,750 --> 01:00:46,750
I know that your secret makes you unable to marry Pin.

726
01:00:47,750 --> 01:00:49,750
But other people don't know this.

727
01:00:54,750 --> 01:00:55,750
Mother.

728
01:00:57,750 --> 01:00:59,750
We've talked about this many times, Tian.

729
01:01:00,750 --> 01:01:02,750
And I won't change my mind.

730
01:01:04,750 --> 01:01:05,750
One more month and a half,

731
01:01:06,750 --> 01:01:08,750
you have to marry Pin.

732
01:01:17,750 --> 01:01:19,750
Mr. Tian's secret.

733
01:01:24,750 --> 01:01:25,750
Tian's secret?

734
01:01:26,050 --> 01:01:26,750
Yes, Madam.

735
01:01:27,750 --> 01:01:28,750
Madam Li talked to Mr. Tian that

736
01:01:29,750 --> 01:01:31,750
his secret made him unable to love Lady Pin.

737
01:01:32,750 --> 01:01:34,750
It's probably related to what Dong said before he died.

738
01:01:36,750 --> 01:01:40,750
Or was that secret really what caused Dong to die?

739
01:01:42,750 --> 01:01:43,750
Mud.

740
01:01:44,750 --> 01:01:47,750
Does Tian hide his lover?

741
01:01:49,750 --> 01:01:50,750
As far as I can see, he has no one.

742
01:01:51,750 --> 01:01:54,750
He works hard every day.

743
01:01:55,250 --> 01:01:56,750
I didn't see any woman around him.

744
01:01:59,750 --> 01:02:02,750
The secret that prevents him to marry Lady Pin.

745
01:02:05,750 --> 01:02:07,750
What's the secret, Tian?

746
01:02:15,750 --> 01:02:19,750
I told you I had a few treasures left.

747
01:02:20,750 --> 01:02:22,750
You don't think that it will be this few, right?

748
01:02:44,750 --> 01:02:47,750
But you have a vast land with you now.

749
01:02:48,750 --> 01:02:49,750
I might sell it for a good price.

750
01:02:50,750 --> 01:02:52,750
It is a waste land.

751
01:02:53,750 --> 01:02:56,750
Father and I never took care of it. The location is far.

752
01:02:57,750 --> 01:03:00,750
There was an acquaintance selling it to my father in the past.

753
01:03:01,250 --> 01:03:02,750
My father pitied him, so he bought it.

754
01:03:05,750 --> 01:03:08,750
If we can't sell the treasures and land,

755
01:03:09,750 --> 01:03:10,750
we have to find another way.

756
01:03:11,750 --> 01:03:14,750
I think there must be a way that we can earn more money.

757
01:03:16,750 --> 01:03:18,750
I make delicious desserts, or...

758
01:03:19,750 --> 01:03:21,750
Should I sell desserts?

759
01:03:22,150 --> 01:03:22,750
Hey, we need hundreds of thousands.

760
01:03:25,750 --> 01:03:26,750
If you make desserts, you have to make hundreds of thousands of pieces to be enough.

761
01:03:30,750 --> 01:03:31,750
That's true.

762
01:03:32,750 --> 01:03:33,750
I'm really crazy.

763
01:03:34,750 --> 01:03:36,750
Who sells desserts to pay debts?

764
01:03:37,750 --> 01:03:38,750
It's only a month and a half.

765
01:03:40,750 --> 01:03:41,750
Don't lose hope.

766
01:03:42,750 --> 01:03:44,750
I think we need to help each other out.

767
01:03:45,750 --> 01:03:47,750
There must be some way that we can redeem the palace back.

768
01:03:48,350 --> 01:03:48,750
Believe me?

769
01:03:49,750 --> 01:03:50,750
And if we can't?

770
01:03:51,750 --> 01:03:53,750
Just get married to Tian.

771
01:03:55,750 --> 01:03:57,750
It's good. That's easy.

772
01:03:59,750 --> 01:04:01,750
I'm kidding.

773
01:04:02,250 --> 01:04:03,750
I'm kidding too.

774
01:04:04,050 --> 01:04:04,750
I won't get married.

775
01:04:05,250 --> 01:04:07,750
Though a month and a half is difficult,

776
01:04:08,750 --> 01:04:09,750
I will try my best.

777
01:04:10,750 --> 01:04:13,750
It’s better than marrying and living with someone I don’t love for the rest of my life.

778
01:04:17,750 --> 01:04:19,750
I'm so happy hearing this.

779
01:04:20,750 --> 01:04:21,750
I want to take you away now.

780
01:04:22,750 --> 01:04:23,750
Yang.

781
01:04:25,750 --> 01:04:27,750
Let's go. Pack your back now, shall we?

782
01:04:34,750 --> 01:04:38,750
I heard that Madam Li had already talked about the wedding and the bride price.

783
01:04:42,750 --> 01:04:44,750
I don't know if Mr. Ma will be able to stop him.

784
01:04:45,750 --> 01:04:49,750
I didn't see Mr. Ma did anything.

785
01:04:50,450 --> 01:04:52,750
Besides, he also uses you to send news

786
01:04:53,350 --> 01:04:54,750
of what Tian's doing and where he's been to.

787
01:04:55,750 --> 01:04:59,750
As if Mr. Tian will always report to us.

788
01:05:00,750 --> 01:05:02,750
I don't know why he wants to know it.

789
01:05:03,050 --> 01:05:03,750
Idiot.

790
01:05:04,750 --> 01:05:05,750
Think about it.

791
01:05:06,750 --> 01:05:08,750
What would a person like Mr. Ma do?

792
01:05:15,750 --> 01:05:16,750
You're here.

793
01:05:19,750 --> 01:05:20,750
What's the matter?

794
01:05:21,750 --> 01:05:22,750
Mr. Song requests to see you.

795
01:05:29,750 --> 01:05:31,750
I call everyone to come here today

796
01:05:32,750 --> 01:05:34,750
because I have good news to inform you.

797
01:05:35,750 --> 01:05:36,750
In another month and a half,

798
01:05:37,750 --> 01:05:39,750
there will be an auspicious event of Tian.

799
01:05:51,750 --> 01:05:54,750
So I want to take everyone to pay respects to the god

800
01:05:55,750 --> 01:05:58,750
at the Song family's shrine in Chonburi.

801
01:06:07,750 --> 01:06:09,750
So I want everyone to get ready.

802
01:06:10,750 --> 01:06:11,750
We will depart tomorrow.

803
01:06:35,750 --> 01:06:37,750
What did you write?

804
01:06:38,250 --> 01:06:38,750
Don't tell me you wrote a goodbye letter to enter priesthood.

805
01:06:39,750 --> 01:06:42,750
You only want me to be ordained?

806
01:06:43,750 --> 01:06:44,750
Take this.

807
01:06:46,750 --> 01:06:49,750
Take it to Mr. Ma and don't let anyone see this.

808
01:06:53,750 --> 01:06:55,750
It's time for heaven to take my side.

809
01:06:56,050 --> 01:06:57,750
Heaven does not favor wicked.

810
01:06:58,050 --> 01:06:58,750
Nuan!

811
01:06:59,750 --> 01:07:00,750
Why are you mad?

812
01:07:01,750 --> 01:07:02,750
Heaven does not favor the wicked.

813
01:07:03,250 --> 01:07:05,750
But you are good, so heaven has mercy on you.

814
01:07:06,050 --> 01:07:08,750
You want a kick, huh?

815
01:07:10,750 --> 01:07:14,750
I want to wear a black dress to Tian's wedding now.

816
01:07:15,750 --> 01:07:17,750
I can hardly wait for this moment.

817
01:07:24,750 --> 01:07:25,750
Sir.

818
01:07:26,750 --> 01:07:28,750
Mr. Song takes many people to the shrine.

819
01:07:29,750 --> 01:07:30,750
Aren't there too many people?

820
01:07:31,750 --> 01:07:34,750
A lot of people are good. He won't be careful.

821
01:07:35,750 --> 01:07:38,750
We have Chan as a decoy. It will be fine.

822
01:07:39,250 --> 01:07:41,750
Call Jiu for me. I have a job for him.

823
01:07:42,350 --> 01:07:42,750
Yes, Sir.

824
01:07:50,750 --> 01:07:51,750
I have a job for you to do.

825
01:07:52,750 --> 01:07:53,750
This job is very important.

826
01:07:54,750 --> 01:07:56,750
Don't make a mistake.

827
01:08:00,750 --> 01:08:02,750
If you are successful,

828
01:08:03,750 --> 01:08:06,750
I will give you the medicine formula used to treat your sister.

829
01:08:07,750 --> 01:08:10,750
You will be free. You can do whatever you want in the future.

830
01:08:11,750 --> 01:08:15,750
You don't have to take my job in exchange for medicine to cure your sister again.

831
01:08:17,750 --> 01:08:19,750
Just tell me who do you want me to kill.

832
01:08:22,750 --> 01:08:25,750
I want you to kill the Song's eldest son.

833
01:09:10,750 --> 01:09:12,750
Aren't you in love with Pin?

834
01:09:13,250 --> 01:09:13,750
Or you...

835
01:09:14,750 --> 01:09:18,750
Excuse me. Do you know someone named Doctor Qi?

836
01:09:19,750 --> 01:09:20,750
What shall we do?

837
01:09:21,750 --> 01:09:22,750
Who is investigating this?

838
01:09:23,350 --> 01:09:25,750
I won't believe anything until I have evidence.

839
01:09:29,750 --> 01:09:30,750
Do you have anything to tell me?

840
01:09:31,750 --> 01:09:34,750
If he's not dead, your sister will.

841
01:09:35,250 --> 01:09:36,750
Yang, can you call Tian for me?
